headline: 2 Reasons to Watch CAH and 1 to Stay Cautious
summary: Since September 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 85.4%. But one standout stock has more than doubled the market - over the past five years, Cardinal Health has surged 198% to $149.15 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 15.5% in the last six months, beating the S&P by 5.8%.
